{"tid":267073,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人讀緊/讀過Zoology?","createTime":"2017-06-02T03:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:45:33.000Z","uid":83915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4da56c472dfaef301d01cb2f5b27a3a44ca2d1","tid":267073,"uid":83915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:43:36.000Z","msg":"我講緊係major/ degree in zoology <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家係澳洲讀緊大學，諗緊主修咩 <br />\n見到zoology 呢個major 好似幾有趣<br />\n因為自問都真係幾有心同動物相處<br />\n本身都鐘意Biology/ Life Science<br />\n出黎都想做啲可以接觸動物既工作<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔係太清楚career 係咪真係咁好<br />\n我會留係澳洲 應該唔會返香港<br />\n係咪真係有得去zoo 做trainer/ zoologist<br />\n又或者去animal farm 做<br />\n定係畢業既都係搵返其它同呢科無關既工多<br />\n<br />\n唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎任何人禮貌討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00d9375653571f1e5c5d318e3845d5299c69151","tid":267073,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:34:32.000Z","msg":"我都想讀 英國撚 本來year1頭想轉科但係仆佢個街我啱啱好miss左佢第一個assignment唔俾我轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e0206f89a9ee05f94eb49823332873fb42871a","tid":267073,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:36:06.000Z","msg":"不過做zoologist真係好難 你冇多幾個degree都冇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  行頭窄啲野又廣又專門"},{"pid":"33c4887839f7ef0ce3024d04fbf5a8f04fd57117","tid":267073,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"你有本錢做因航嘅董事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f01452333ed044e1a656ec434187280811433","tid":267073,"uid":83915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過做zoologist真係好難 你冇多幾個degree都冇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  行頭窄啲野又廣又專門</blockquote><br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我上網check 咗想做大型Zoo既keeper 係好難 一黎多candidate 佢地好多都係farm/country 大，我地呢啲城市人點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  二黎有degree 之餘要fitness 都好得<br />\n<br />\nZoologist 唔洗講 我諗要真係落field 做好多動物研究都要好高學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係海外加油 共勉之"},{"pid":"f0e9002b30eb6fbcf8bf0787671598fb96f11c97","tid":267073,"uid":83915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有本錢做因航嘅董事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd5fa7e4b09c21f7f2a9562300390a81dbee2cc","tid":267073,"uid":120388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b972e204ed3aca9fd26b77fff470494779716bbe","tid":267073,"uid":120755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"澳洲邊度讀緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72709fa0164aa204f6b711b32ab118685f67435f","tid":267073,"uid":83915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過做zoologist真係好難 你冇多幾個degree都冇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  行頭窄啲野又廣又專門</blockquote><br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我上網check 咗想做大型Zoo既keeper 係好難 一黎多candidate 佢地好多都係farm/country 大，我地呢啲城市人點比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  二黎有degree 之餘要fitness 都好得<br />\n<br />\nZoologist 唔洗講 我諗要真係落field 做好多動物研究都要好高學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係海外加油 共勉之</blockquote><br />\n加油呀，ching去到澳洲讀，